Mangalore Refinery Said to Sell 40,000 Tons of July Diesel to BP

-- B y   P r a t i s h   N a r a y a n a n
-- 
2011-06-02T07:41:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/mangalore-refinery-said-to-sell-40-000-tons-of-july-diesel-to-bp.html
India ’s  Mangalore Refinery &
Petrochemicals Ltd. (MRPL)  sold 40,000 metric tons of gasoil, or
diesel, for loading in July to BP Plc, according to two traders
who participate in the market.  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s largest oil
producer, owns 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  Details of the sale are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
